佢"},{"pid":"aa75cb21c2611697ddcf7c587f24cb5b0be245b3","tid":258011,"uid":9264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T17:11:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Starbucks可以，不過唔係快餐<br />\n<br />\n外國Mcdonalds 都好似可以</blockquote></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"49d240d1b1a6af5c4cf62f24ba229610e7f5889c","tid":258011,"uid":70635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T17:12:30.000Z","msg":"因為信用卡要收手續費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a774a3a1a9c2eed8e87333a094d66b2ee91fec0","tid":258011,"uid":9264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T17:19:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>要做會員+身份認證</blockquote><br />\n唔一定，可以set個nfc/rfid scanner，個客嚟到如果佢已經係有order，個店員只係需要根據返嗰order no.俾個包去個客到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然人手需求可能會少一啲，失業率會輕微上升，但對公司同顧客嚟講應該係好事先啱喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當中如果有咩謬誤請指出<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n使乜nfc/rfid<br />\n用qr code/barcode 咪得<br />\n<br />\ne.g. 當M記有呢個模式<br />\n我用app order 完set 埋幾耐之後要有貨<br />\n比完錢 佢gen 個qr code <br />\n我到時到候就去M記個取餐處搵個staff scan 個barcode<br />\n個staff 就搵返我果袋野食出嚟比我攞走<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然講就好完美<br />\n但係對啲唔肯用腦嘅on9嚟講<br />\n搞啲咁嘅野佢唔會感激你提升效率仲要屌鳩你搞埋啲九唔搭八野嚟煩到佢</blockquote><br />\n使乜又qr code又barcode咁麻煩，毎張m記單都有個order number，好似而家咁就咁對返個number咪得"},{"pid":"0c1bb361177a2f33963bcf8215c3281bf39e272e","tid":258011,"uid":91146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T17:25:59.000Z","msg":"大陸kfc 有 <br />\n開gps 睇下路程<br />\n10分鐘之內步行距離可落單<br />\n比menu 你簡 之後微信支付寶比錢<br />\n錢已收 你攞唔攞隨你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee9dcced56c17b9c8d8d75c8c626bfbeb3e187b","tid":258011,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"